name: Gubinelli-Hofmanova global solutions
source: Gubinelli, M., Hofmanova, M. (2019). Global solutions to elliptic and parabolic Phi^4 models in Euclidean space. Communications in Mathematical Physics, 368(3), 1201-1266. arXiv:1810.01700. Proposition 2.3 provides L^p moment bounds for Wick-ordered powers under the Phi^4_3 measure.
